            "name": "Two Actions",
            "subtype": "action_type",
            "type": "stat_block_section"
          },
          "effect": "You and the crew Stride, with a maximum distance equal to the slowest crew member\u2019s Speed, then make a melee Strike with the drilling ram against a structure or unattended, stationary object. This Strike deals piercing damage equal to 5d8 + the highest Strength modifier among members of the crew.",
