          "ability_type": "offensive",
          "action_type": {
            "name": "One Action",
            "subtype": "action_type",
            "type": "stat_block_section"
          },
          "effect": "The drill whirls to life, burrowing into the structure or object it struck, which has its Hardness reduced by 5 (minimum 0) for the drilling ram\u2019s next Strike. Adamantine structures and objects aren\u2019t affected.",
